                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-2">CARGADOR FRONTAL</h3>
                    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Carga, acarreo corto, abastecimiento y maniobras en patios de operación.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-variant border-2 border-outline-variant group overflow-hidden">
                <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
